\]

---

**5. Collector area required**

\[
A = \frac{\dot Q_{\text{in}}}{I_{\odot}}
   = \frac{6.47\times10^{3}\;\text{W}}{3.33\times10^{2}\;\text{W m}^{-2}}
   \approx 1.94\times10^{1}\;\text{m}^{2}
\]

